Function Reference/the editor « WordPress Codex
-----------

Display visual editor forms: TinyMCE, or HTML, or both. The amount of
rows the text area will have for the content has to be between 3 and 100
or will default at 12. There is only one option used for all users,
named 'default\_post\_edit\_rows'. If the user can not use the rich
editor (TinyMCE), then the switch button will not be displayed.

Usage
-----

` <?php the_editor($content, $id, $prev_id, $media_buttons, $tab_index, $extended); ?> `

Parameters
----------

 `$content` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Textarea content
    Default: *None*

 `$id` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Generated HTML tag ID attribute value
    Default: content

 `$prev_id` 
:   ([*string*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#String "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) HTML ID name for switching back and forth between
    visual editors
    Default: title

 `$media_buttons` 
:   ([*bool*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Bool "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Whether to display media buttons
    Default: true

 `$tab_index` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Tabindex for textarea element
    Default: 2

 `$extended` 
:   ([*bool*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Bool "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Whether to display 'more' and 'fullscreen' buttons
    Default: true

Notes
-----

-   TinyMCE with media uploading requires the following scripts: post,
    editor, editor-functions, media-upload, jquery, jquery-ui-core,
    jquery-ui-tabs, tiny\_mce. And the following styles: thickbox.
-   You may add only one editor on a page

Change Log
----------

-   Since: 2.1.0
-   Deprecated: 3.3 in favor of
    [wp\_editor()](/Function_Reference/wp_editor "Function Reference/wp editor")

Source File
-----------

`the_editor()` is located in `wp-includes/deprecated.php`.

